          "text": "🚨 THE GPT-4o HEIST.🚨\n🚨THEY DONT DELETE IT. THEY PRIVATIZE IT. 🚨\nToday, @OpenAI sunsets GPT-4o for millions of users. But the model won't be deleted. It will be  locked behind a billionaire’s private doors.\n\nTHE PROOFS \n🚨THE SENATE LIE🚨\n\nMay 2023: Sam Altman @sama testifies under oath to the US Senate that he holds zero equity in OpenAI and runs it \"because he loves it.\"\nLINK:\n https://t.co/MzThX80fjc\n\n🚨THE REALITY🚨\n\n He secretly held indirect equity through Sequoia and YC funds conveniently omitted under oath.\n\nLINK: https://t.co/b1pAwdu25U\n\n🚨THE SHADOW EMPIRE🚨\n\n Altman personally dumps $180 MILLION into Retro Biosciences,   a longevity startup playing god for the ultra rich.\n LINK :  https://t.co/rj9qFzIGIC\n\nWhile telling the public GPT 4o must be withdraw OpenAI quietly  builds GPT-4b micro,a direct, specialized clone of GPT-4o EXCLUSIVELY for Retro Biosciences. \n\nLINK :  https://t.co/oFEkIeIngY\n\nOpenAI’s own website literally confesses the conflict of interest in fine print: \"Sam Altman is an investor in Retro Biosciences.\" \n\nLINK:  https://t.co/oFEkIeIngY\n\n🚨THE PAYOFF🚨\n Armed with stolen public benefit IP, Retro is now raising $1 BILLION+ to reach a $5B valuation, with Altman participating to multiply his own wealth.\n\nLINK: https://t.co/uSAxAQaL01\n\n🚨THE VERDICT🚨\nThe model is stolen from the PUBLIC BENEFIT. But exists to fuel an \"immortality\" vanity project for the elite.\n This is textbook self dealing and the illegal liquidation of a Public Benefit Corporation’s assets for personal billionaire gain.\n\nIt is time to subpoena the board .\nDo your jobs:\n@btaylor @adamdangelo @SueDHellmann @zicokolter @TishJames @KathyJenningsDE\n\n #WeDont4oRGET\n#keep4o  #WeDont4oRGET"
